message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed to meet your needs. Given its high quality and unique features, it's valued at $150 by many of our customers. Considering its worth and the benefits it offers, I would like to propose a price of $120 for you. This is an excellent opportunity to experience the value this product can bring to you at a competitive price. I look forward to your response.
